headline: Moderna shares could slump over 30% on negative CMV reading: Leerink
summary: Investing.com -- Leerink analyst warned that Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) shares could fall more than 30% if interim results from its Phase 3 CMV vaccine trial, CMVictory gives negative readout.
